@startuml CreateTeacherAccount
|Admin|
start
:1. Open create user form;
:2. Fill in teacher info;
:3. Select "Teacher" role;
:4. Submit form;
|AdminPanel|
:5. Create teacher account;
|AdminController|
:6. Save user with Teacher role;
:7. Send activation or temp password email;
|EmailService|
:8. Confirmation of email sent;
|AdminController|
:9. Return success message;
|AdminPanel|
:10. Display account created confirmation;
stop
@enduml